##DESCRIPTION
## Calculate the effective resistance of a network of resistors
##ENDDESCRIPTION

## DBsubject(Electricity and Magnetism)
## DBchapter(Electric Circuits)
## DBsection(Kirchhoff's laws)
## Date(2 February 2018)
